    <item>
      <title>随着竞争对手的崛起，苹果iPhone面临自新冠疫情以来最严重的下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apple-s-iphone-shipments-plunge-10-as-android-rivals-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 的 iPhone 出货量在 3 月份结束的季度中下滑近 10%，低于预期，反映出尽管智能手机行业出现更广泛的反弹，但在中国的销售却疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apple-s-iphone-shipments-plunge-10-as-android-rivals-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
